Hellplague:

Hellplague heard the commotion and walked toward it.  She saw the unidentified bot in the cabin and threw up both arms, arming her disruptors and taking aim on him.
&quot;What do you want here?  Why do you intrude in our ship?  You cannot leave now, you won&#39;t be contacting the Maximals, you&#39;ll either die now or be taken prisoners, either choice, it does not bother me.&quot;
She hoped this commotuion didn&#39;t wake up Malice.  He would surely be cranky, and nothing good would come from it.

