Celeron, after being startled that there were people onboard, took a
step back and held up his arm, which made a sound like a camera flash
charging.

&quot;Ah....so I see there are people here.....how interesting....&quot; he said
as he dropped the part in his other hand that had once been attached
to a computer in that room.  &quot;I was just taking a look around&quot; said
Celeron in a unnervingly calm voice, &quot;Just looking at all the
intersting STUFF you got laying around here.....you see, I thought
this ship was abandoned.  My mistake.  I will be on my way now...&quot; he
said this but took no action toward leaving and still stood there
pointing his arm at Blacknightmare&#39;s gun.


